Cell["\<\
The result makes sense and is the one with the highest probability according \
to the predictor. One can look at other options with lower probability which, \
in this particular example, seem to make less sense than \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]the\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.780150926930716*^9, 
  3.780150989968624*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b30ce0b6-5cf9-4eeb-86ca-\
583e0ae4d66e"],

